data.description: A perfect location for exactly what you're feeling- a country drive head south or feeling big city stay on the pavement and head north.    This acreage property has all the convenience of town without the hustle of city life.   Big stars at night and all the good stuff  like birds singing but close enough to grab a gallon of milk 5 minutes from home.    Space to roam inside and out.   And a new roof in 2023!   The spacious footprint of this home allows for plenty of privacy and yet so many functional areas for gathering together and celebrating life.   Consider yourself home and plan to make countless memories inside and out! (AMA)
